sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User
  participant Agent as Claude Code / Agent
  participant Hook as PreToolUse Hook
  participant CM as Context Mode (MCP Server)
  participant SB as Sandbox Subprocess
  participant Tools as External Tools/CLIs
  participant KB as SQLite FTS5 KB

  User->>Agent: Task / Request
  Agent->>Hook: Invoke MCP tool
  Hook->>CM: Route tool call + args
  CM->>SB: Spawn isolated subprocess
  SB->>Tools: Execute (Playwright/gh/logs/etc.)
  Tools-->>SB: Raw output (large blobs)
  SB->>SB: Extract/transform -> small stdout
  SB-->>CM: stdout only (compact artifact)
  CM-->>Agent: Compact result (<~1KB)

  opt Fetch and index docs
    Agent->>CM: fetch_and_index(url)
    CM->>SB: Fetch HTML -> Markdown
    SB->>KB: Chunk by headings, preserve code blocks
    KB-->>CM: Indexed content
    CM-->>Agent: Index confirmation
  end

  opt Search KB
    Agent->>CM: search(query)
    CM->>KB: BM25 search (FTS5)
    KB-->>CM: Exact snippets + heading path
    CM-->>Agent: Snippets (not raw pages)
  end
